rows.label: tlk45350141_03_msg0001
rows.name: Well, well. If it isn't our new leader.

rows.label: tlk45350141_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Even with Vandham gone, the job
requests just keep coming in.

rows.label: tlk45350141_03_msg0003
rows.name:
And until such time as they dry up,
I will continue to perform my duties
just as I always have.

rows.label: tlk45350141_03_msg0004
rows.name:
You can count on me to fill you in
on the jobs we currently have going.
